---
title: Smoky Adobo Chicken Tacos with Mango Slaw & Lime Crema
description: Chipotle peppers are great and all, but let's not forget about the tangy, firey sauce that comes along with them. Adobo sauce makes the perfect one-ingredient marinade - especially if you love deep, smokey flavors. Cool lime crema, creamy avocado, and tangy mango slaw help to balance out the heat in these irresistible tacos.
